{"word":"ἀνάπλοος","slug":"ἀνάπλοος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀνάπλοος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀναπλέω'><el>ἀναπλέω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a sailing upstream</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>a putting out</i> to sea, <b><a href='S:Polybius'>Polyb.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}